<p>For years I’ve been bemoaning Apple’s failure to use interesting non-muted colors on the iPhone Pro. It appears this year Apple may be&nbsp;<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/25/iphone-17-pros-rumored-new-orange-color-confirmed/">calling my bluff</a>&nbsp;with an orange iPhone Pro. Orange!</p>



<p>If true, it will be hard to put that beauty in a case.</p>



